---
import Header from '../components/Header.astro';
import Icon from '../components/Icon.astro';
import { approach, consultationHref, email, expectations, phoneDisplay, phoneHref } from '../data/site';
import '../styles/global.css';
const year = new Date().getFullYear();
const schema = { '@context':'https://schema.org','@type':'Person',name:'Nathalie Bose-Silver',jobTitle:'Catholic Spiritual Director',telephone:'+1-321-231-0058',email,areaServed:['Oviedo, Florida','Winter Park, Florida'],knowsLanguage:['English','Spanish'] };
const base = import.meta.env.BASE_URL.replace(/\/$/, '');
---
<!doctype html><html lang="en"><head><meta charset="UTF-8"/><meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width"/><title>Nathalie Bose-Silver | Catholic Spiritual Director</title><meta name="description" content="Compassionate Catholic spiritual direction in English and Spanish. Begin with a free 30-minute consultation."/><meta property="og:title" content="Nathalie Bose-Silver | Spiritual Direction"/><meta property="og:description" content="A prayerful space to notice grace and discern your path."/><meta property="og:type" content="website"/><meta property="og:image" content="/images/spiritual-journey/spiritual-journey-logo.png"/><script is:inline type="application/ld+json" set:html={JSON.stringify(schema)}/></head>
<body id="top"><a class="skip" href="#main">Skip to content</a><Header/>
<main id="main">
  <section class="hero">
    <div class="hero-index" aria-hidden="true"><i></i><small>Welcome</small></div>
    <div class="hero-copy"><p class="kicker">Catholic spiritual direction · English & Spanish</p><h1>A quieter way to hear what your <em>heart</em> already knows.</h1><p class="hero-lead">Step away from the noise. Enter a confidential, prayerful conversation where you can notice God’s movement and meet your life with clarity, courage, and grace.</p><div class="hero-actions"><a class="primary-link" href={consultationHref}>Free 30-minute conversation <span>↗</span></a><a class="text-link" href={phoneHref}>{phoneDisplay} <span>→</span></a></div></div>
    <div class="hero-visual"><div class="orbit orbit-one"></div><div class="orbit orbit-two"></div><img src={`${base}/images/spiritual-journey/spiritual-journey-logo.png`} width="1024" height="1024" alt="Spiritual Journey emblem featuring a winding path, butterflies, hands holding a flame, and a dove."/><p><span>✦</span>A sacred pause<br/>for your unfolding path</p></div>
    <a class="scroll-cue" href="#practice"><span>Scroll to explore</span><i>↓</i></a>
  </section>

  <section class="manifesto" id="practice">
    <div class="butterfly butterfly-1" aria-hidden="true">
      <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M12 10c-.7-2-3-5.5-6-5.5C3 4.5 1 6.5 1 9.5c0 3 2.5 5.5 5.5 6.5-.5 1-1.5 2.5-3 3.5 0 0 2-.5 3.5-2 .5.5 1 1 1.5 1s1-.5 1.5-1c1.5 1.5 3.5 2 3.5 2-1.5-1-2.5-2.5-3-3.5 3-1 5.5-3.5 5.5-6.5 0-3-2-5-5-5-3 0-5.3 3.5-6 5.5z"/></svg>
    </div>
    <div class="butterfly butterfly-2" aria-hidden="true">
      <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M12 10c-.7-2-3-5.5-6-5.5C3 4.5 1 6.5 1 9.5c0 3 2.5 5.5 5.5 6.5-.5 1-1.5 2.5-3 3.5 0 0 2-.5 3.5-2 .5.5 1 1 1.5 1s1-.5 1.5-1c1.5 1.5 3.5 2 3.5 2-1.5-1-2.5-2.5-3-3.5 3-1 5.5-3.5 5.5-6.5 0-3-2-5-5-5-3 0-5.3 3.5-6 5.5z"/></svg>
    </div>
    <div class="butterfly butterfly-3" aria-hidden="true">
      <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M12 10c-.7-2-3-5.5-6-5.5C3 4.5 1 6.5 1 9.5c0 3 2.5 5.5 5.5 6.5-.5 1-1.5 2.5-3 3.5 0 0 2-.5 3.5-2 .5.5 1 1 1.5 1s1-.5 1.5-1c1.5 1.5 3.5 2 3.5 2-1.5-1-2.5-2.5-3-3.5 3-1 5.5-3.5 5.5-6.5 0-3-2-5-5-5-3 0-5.3 3.5-6 5.5z"/></svg>
    </div>
    <div class="butterfly butterfly-4" aria-hidden="true">
      <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M12 10c-.7-2-3-5.5-6-5.5C3 4.5 1 6.5 1 9.5c0 3 2.5 5.5 5.5 6.5-.5 1-1.5 2.5-3 3.5 0 0 2-.5 3.5-2 .5.5 1 1 1.5 1s1-.5 1.5-1c1.5 1.5 3.5 2 3.5 2-1.5-1-2.5-2.5-3-3.5 3-1 5.5-3.5 5.5-6.5 0-3-2-5-5-5-3 0-5.3 3.5-6 5.5z"/></svg>
    </div>
    <div class="butterfly butterfly-5" aria-hidden="true">
      <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M12 10c-.7-2-3-5.5-6-5.5C3 4.5 1 6.5 1 9.5c0 3 2.5 5.5 5.5 6.5-.5 1-1.5 2.5-3 3.5 0 0 2-.5 3.5-2 .5.5 1 1 1.5 1s1-.5 1.5-1c1.5 1.5 3.5 2 3.5 2-1.5-1-2.5-2.5-3-3.5 3-1 5.5-3.5 5.5-6.5 0-3-2-5-5-5-3 0-5.3 3.5-6 5.5z"/></svg>
    </div>
    <div class="butterfly butterfly-6" aria-hidden="true">
      <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M12 10c-.7-2-3-5.5-6-5.5C3 4.5 1 6.5 1 9.5c0 3 2.5 5.5 5.5 6.5-.5 1-1.5 2.5-3 3.5 0 0 2-.5 3.5-2 .5.5 1 1 1.5 1s1-.5 1.5-1c1.5 1.5 3.5 2 3.5 2-1.5-1-2.5-2.5-3-3.5 3-1 5.5-3.5 5.5-6.5 0-3-2-5-5-5-3 0-5.3 3.5-6 5.5z"/></svg>
    </div>
    <div class="section-number">The practice</div><div class="manifesto-title"><p>Spiritual direction is</p><h2>Not advice.<br/>Not therapy.<br/><em>Sacred attention.</em></h2><figure class="practice-image"><img src="/images/spiritual-journey/spiritual-practice.png" alt="An open Bible, a simple wooden rosary, and a warm lit candle on a rustic wooden table, suggesting a prayerful and sacred space." loading="lazy"/><figcaption>A space to listen beyond the noise.</figcaption></figure></div><div class="manifesto-copy"><p>It is a conversation centered on your relationship with God—a place to slow down, reflect, pray, and become attentive to grace in ordinary life.</p><p>Nathalie does not diagnose or hand you answers. She accompanies you as you recognize the Divine within and around you, and discern the path that is already unfolding.</p><aside>“A spiritual director is one who helps another to recognize and follow the inspirations of grace.”</aside></div></section>

  <section class="path-section" id="journey"><div class="path-heading"><div><span class="section-number">The journey</span><h2>Four movements.<br/>One unfolding path.</h2></div><p>Monthly, one-hour conversations shaped around your life—not a formula.</p></div><div class="path-layout"><div class="path-line" aria-hidden="true"><span class="path-progress"></span></div>{expectations.map(([icon,title,text],i)=><article class="path-step"><div class="step-icon"><Icon name={icon}/></div><div><h3>{title}</h3><p>{text}</p></div></article>)}</div></section>

  <section class="approach"><div class="approach-sticky"><span class="section-number">The approach</span><h2>Held with care.<br/>Guided by grace.</h2><p>Every session is an invitation to pause and listen deeply to what is moving within your heart.</p></div><div class="approach-panels">{approach.map(([title,text],i)=><article><h3>{title}</h3><p>{text}</p></article>)}</div></section>

  <section class="profile" id="nathalie"><figure class="profile-mark profile-photo"><img src="/images/spiritual-journey/profile-pic.png" alt="Portrait of Nathalie Bose-Silver smiling in an orange jacket." loading="lazy"/><figcaption>Compassionate presence · Prayerful listening</figcaption></figure><div class="profile-copy"><span class="section-number">Your companion</span><h2>Meet Nathalie<br/>Bose-Silver.</h2><p class="profile-intro">A certified professional spiritual director rooted in the Catholic faith and open to the unique sacred story of every person.</p><div class="profile-columns"><p>Nathalie completed the Sacred Presence Program at San Pedro Center, a ministry of the Diocese of Orlando, and is a member of Spiritual Directors International.</p><p>Her experience includes adult and youth faith formation and founding a nonprofit rosary-making ministry supporting deeper devotion and prayer.</p></div><div class="credentials"><span>Certified Spiritual Director</span><span>English & Spanish</span><span>SDI Member</span></div></div></section>

  <section class="meeting" id="meeting-section">
    <div class="meeting-intro">
      <span class="section-number">Where we meet</span>
      <h2>Wherever you can<br/>be fully present.</h2>
    </div>
    
    <div class="tabs-container">
      <div class="tabs-nav" role="tablist" aria-label="Meeting options">
        <button class="tab-btn active" role="tab" aria-selected="true" aria-controls="panel-zoom" id="tab-zoom">
          <Icon name="video" />
          <span>Zoom</span>
        </button>
        <button class="tab-btn" role="tab" aria-selected="false" aria-controls="panel-phone" id="tab-phone">
          <Icon name="phone" />
          <span>Phone</span>
        </button>
        <button class="tab-btn" role="tab" aria-selected="false" aria-controls="panel-inperson" id="tab-inperson">
          <Icon name="place" />
          <span>In person</span>
        </button>
        <div class="tabs-indicator"></div>
      </div>

      <div class="tabs-window">
        <div class="tabs-slider">
          <div class="tab-panel" id="panel-zoom" role="tabpanel" aria-labelledby="tab-zoom">
            <div class="panel-visual">
              <div class="visual-circle circle-zoom">
                <Icon name="video" />
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="panel-content">
              <h3>Video Session</h3>
              <p>Meet face-to-face from a private, comfortable place of your choosing. Online sessions offer flexibility and ease of scheduling from the privacy of your home or office.</p>
              <a href="#contact" class="panel-action">Schedule a Zoom session <span>→</span></a>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="tab-panel" id="panel-phone" role="tabpanel" aria-labelledby="tab-phone">
            <div class="panel-visual">
              <div class="visual-circle circle-phone">
                <Icon name="phone" />
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="panel-content">
              <h3>Phone Call</h3>
              <p>A simple and accessible way to connect from wherever you feel at ease. Ideal for those who prefer to walk, sit in nature, or simply find speaking without a screen more reflective.</p>
              <a href="#contact" class="panel-action">Schedule a phone session <span>→</span></a>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="tab-panel" id="panel-inperson" role="tabpanel" aria-labelledby="tab-inperson">
            <div class="panel-visual">
              <div class="visual-circle circle-inperson">
                <Icon name="place" />
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="panel-content">
              <h3>In Person</h3>
              <p>Meet in Oviedo or Winter Park, Florida. A quiet, dedicated space designed for deep listening, prayerful stillness, and personal connection.</p>
              <a href="#contact" class="panel-action">Schedule in-person <span>→</span></a>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <script>
    document.addEventListener('DOMContentLoaded', () => {
      const tabsContainer = document.querySelector('.tabs-container');
      if (!tabsContainer) return;

      const tabBtns = Array.from(tabsContainer.querySelectorAll('.tab-btn')) as HTMLButtonElement[];
      const tabsIndicator = tabsContainer.querySelector('.tabs-indicator') as HTMLElement;
      const tabsSlider = tabsContainer.querySelector('.tabs-slider') as HTMLElement;
      let currentIndex = 0;
      let autoplayInterval: any;

      function updateTabs(btn: HTMLButtonElement) {
        const index = tabBtns.indexOf(btn);
        if (index === -1) return;
        currentIndex = index;

        tabBtns.forEach(b => {
          b.classList.remove('active');
          b.setAttribute('aria-selected', 'false');
        });

        btn.classList.add('active');
        btn.setAttribute('aria-selected', 'true');

        if (tabsIndicator) {
          const isMobile = window.innerWidth <= 900;
          if (isMobile) {
            tabsIndicator.style.height = '';
            tabsIndicator.style.top = '6px';
            tabsIndicator.style.bottom = '6px';
            tabsIndicator.style.width = `${btn.offsetWidth}px`;
            tabsIndicator.style.transform = `translateX(${btn.offsetLeft}px)`;
          } else {
            tabsIndicator.style.width = '';
            tabsIndicator.style.left = '8px';
            tabsIndicator.style.right = '8px';
            tabsIndicator.style.height = `${btn.offsetHeight}px`;
            tabsIndicator.style.transform = `translateY(${btn.offsetTop}px)`;
          }
        }

        const targetId = btn.getAttribute('aria-controls');
        const targetPanel = document.getElementById(targetId || '');
        if (targetPanel && tabsSlider) {
          // Translate vertically
          tabsSlider.style.transform = `translateY(-${index * 33.3333}%)`;
        }
      }

      function nextTab() {
        const nextIndex = (currentIndex + 1) % tabBtns.length;
        updateTabs(tabBtns[nextIndex]);
      }

      // Start autoplay
      autoplayInterval = setInterval(nextTab, 10000);

      tabBtns.forEach(btn => {
        btn.addEventListener('click', () => {
          // Clear autoplay on manual click
          clearInterval(autoplayInterval);
          updateTabs(btn);
        });
      });

      // Init positioning
      setTimeout(() => {
        const activeBtn = tabsContainer.querySelector('.tab-btn.active') as HTMLButtonElement;
        if (activeBtn) {
          updateTabs(activeBtn);
        }
      }, 150);

      window.addEventListener('resize', () => {
        const currentActive = tabsContainer.querySelector('.tab-btn.active') as HTMLButtonElement;
        if (currentActive) {
          updateTabs(currentActive);
        }
      });
    });
  </script>

  <section class="contact" id="contact"><div class="contact-symbol" aria-hidden="true">✦</div><p>Begin with a complimentary conversation</p><h2>Perhaps your next step<br/>is simply to <em>begin.</em></h2><div class="contact-actions"><a href={consultationHref}>Email Nathalie <span>↗</span></a><a href={phoneHref}>Call {phoneDisplay}</a></div><div class="contact-meta"><span>{email}</span><span>English & Spanish</span><span>Zoom · Phone · In person</span></div></section>
  <a href="#top" id="back-to-top" class="back-to-top" aria-label="Back to top">
    <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M4 12l1.41 1.41L11 7.83V20h2V7.83l5.58 5.59L20 12l-8-8z"/></svg>
  </a>
</main>
<footer><div><strong>Nathalie Bose-Silver</strong><span>Catholic Spiritual Director</span></div><nav><a href="#practice">Practice</a><a href="#journey">Journey</a><a href="#nathalie">About</a><a href="#contact">Contact</a></nav><p>© {year} Nathalie Bose-Silver.<br/>Spiritual direction is not a substitute for counseling, psychotherapy, medical care, or emergency services.</p></footer>
<script>
  import '../scripts/animations';

  const backToTop = document.getElementById('back-to-top');
  window.addEventListener('scroll', () => {
    if (window.scrollY > 400) {
      backToTop?.classList.add('visible');
    } else {
      backToTop?.classList.remove('visible');
    }
  });
</script></body></html>
